                  , and being employed and entrusted by them to receive money, notes, bills, and other securities, on their account, by virtue of such employment, did on the 27th of May, receive a bankers draft, value 10 l. 10 s. and that he afterwards feloniously did secrete, embezzle, and steal the same
            </rs>.</p>
