            . I am clerk to Rider and Cherry. I applied to Mr. De Fontaine for this bill, and then I learned he had paid it with a check to the prisoner; neither that check nor the amount ever came into my hands upon the account of my employers.</p>
               <p>MR. 
               <persName id="t18151025-112-person989">
